## Interactive Dashboard
Built at [dashboard/](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/index.html) — 3 files ([index.html](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/index.html), [style.css](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/style.css), [app.js](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/remitaplus/dashboard/app.js))

### Features
- **5 tabs**: Overview, Incident Analysis, KDSG Impact, Remediation, Public Advisory
- Premium dark-mode with animated severity bars and pulsing threat indicators
- Animated KPI counters (3TB, 800GB KYC, 35K passwords, 3 databases)
- Interactive remediation checklist with localStorage persistence
- Live clock and evidence screenshot gallery

